{"tid":565272,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫春啦！！！","createTime":"2018-02-18T19:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T00:58:56.000Z","uid":20750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32df2194e76d6817ad3a33df0f6bc7fa3204677b","tid":565272,"uid":20750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:28:21.000Z","msg":"因為之前好唔開心<br />\n所以叫咗兩個post春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係叫春頂籠係令你暫時抒發到<br />\n你一靜落嚟就會繼續喊，繼續唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而主觀嘅心態，同客觀嘅現實都係改變唔到<br />\n我亦都拎住部電話瞓咗喺床幾日<br />\n突然諗起呢張圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/q2Ka9dm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq2Ka9dm.jpg&h=8d4ddc4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以決定改變氣場！發放正能量！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有乜負能量即管擺低，等我嘗試發射正能量<br />\n或者有咩開心野分享下！<br />\n雖然可能會早洩/射唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係發洩鳩叫鬧我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">屌其實我係想有人keep 住同我講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仍然好辛苦</span>"},{"pid":"c662b9d89e61bed7ba755efeb1a653c9f05f4f45","tid":565272,"uid":73909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"要keep 住叫"},{"pid":"787f978e57caa034f1ffb384b89e4345bc5a8baf","tid":565272,"uid":20750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c662b9d89e61bed7ba755efeb1a653c9f05f4f45","tid":565272,"uid":73909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"要keep 住叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T19:31:09.000Z","msg":"叫嚟冇用㗎<br />\n要叫我陪你叫！<br />\n<strong><sp